[h1]Build your Own Precursor & Ascended Modifiers[/h1]

Extension to [url=https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=865040033]Guilli's Planet Modifiers[/url]

What's the point of having Mega Engineering and Mastery Of Nature if you can't use it to really improve your own planets?

The Precursors aren't that special, after all, their empires have all collapsed.

Why should the Fallen Empires get all the utopian modifiers?

This mod allows you to add most of the Precursor Planetary Modifiers and the Fallen Empire Modifiers from Guilli's Planet Modifiers to your own planets.

To add precursor modifiers you need Mega Engineering and the Mastery of Nature Ascension Perk

To add utopian modifiers you need the above and various levels of the Cosmogenesis Crisis

They are accessed via 2 planetary decisions that become visible when you get Mega Engineering and Cosmogenesis

If you have modifier scaling on in Guilli's it will also scale the cost, which starts at "a lot"

Some modifiers aren't on the list, like "precursor ruins" or "crashed orbital" as they don't make sense, and you have to overlook that a few of the descriptions of the functional ones include "ruins", I'm not renaming Guilli's work just to make it fit better when built.

